WEBVTT

00:03:27.215 --> 00:03:30.613
I jo vaig respondre: "Increïble, 
en què et gastaràs la teva part?"

00:03:30.613 --> 00:03:33.783
Va dir: "En propietats immobiliàries.
I tu?"

00:03:34.133 --> 00:03:37.180
Hi vaig pensar una bona estona...

00:03:38.925 --> 00:03:40.564
I vaig dir: "En una paraula:

00:03:41.632 --> 00:03:42.783
Hummus."

00:03:42.807 --> 00:03:45.988
(Rialles)

00:03:48.261 --> 00:03:49.611
"S'està expandint.

00:03:49.611 --> 00:03:51.018
(Rialles)

00:03:51.395 --> 00:03:53.041
Era al supermercat l'altre dia

00:03:53.065 --> 00:03:55.118
i n'hi havia 30 varietats diferents.

00:03:55.142 --> 00:03:58.039
També pots tallar pastanagues,
i sucar-les-hi.

00:03:58.063 --> 00:03:59.919
Ho has provat mai, Solomon?"

00:03:59.943 --> 00:04:01.943
(Rialles)